# 8. Add Automatic Pipeline DAG

Instead of sequential scripts, define a **DAG pipeline**.

Tools commonly used:

| Tool           | Purpose                 |
| -------------- | ----------------------- |
| ZenML          | ML pipeline framework   |
| Kedro          | production ML pipelines |
| Prefect        | orchestration           |
| Apache Airflow | production scheduling   |

But since you're creating a **template**, a lightweight internal pipeline is better.

