# 11. If You Want to Take This Even Further (Very Powerful)

You can convert this into an **agentic ML system**.

Example agents:

| Agent            | Role                       |
| ---------------- | -------------------------- |
| Data Agent       | validates dataset          |
| Feature Agent    | generates features         |
| Training Agent   | trains models              |
| Evaluation Agent | compares models            |
| Packaging Agent  | builds deployable artifact |

Now your template becomes a **self-operating ML factory**.

